<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Ilog cut to buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Ilog cut to buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Cowen &amp; Co said analyst Drew Brosseau downgraded Ilog SA to buy from strong buy.</p>
<p>-- shares dropped 3-7/8 to 3-1/8.</p>
<p>-- on Wednesday, company said it expects to report a loss of $1 million or less for the third quarter ended March 31.</p>
<p>-- company, which provides advanced software components, said revenues for the quarter will be below $9 million.</p>
<p>-- analyst not immediately available for comment.</p>
</text>
